snippet.title: swingmania Alpha v0.25 teaser
snippet.description: swingmania is an upcoming vr rhythm game focused at competitive ranked play, customizability, ultra high performance and cats! its still early in development. support for custom content (custom slicers, notes, environments) was just added and this is a quick trailer to show it
